article_title: CVS Health Retains PBM Clients And Revenue Jumps 20%

article_metadata.description: CVS Health’s revenue soared nearly 20 percent thanks largely to a big jump in revenue from its pharmacy benefit management business, which helps employers manage prescription costs.
article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen
